originalText.text:
I would not recommend this lawyer to anyone. He is highly unprofessional and attends to you as if you are bothering him and he's doing the client a favor noentheless he eats because of his clients. I called earlier today and was inquiring about their office but instead he responded with, "the attorney is not in call back" and never responded to my questions which were:
1. How much is the fee for a living will?
2. What does the attorney provide in the living will?

If I could give this place a 0 I would gladly. Don't waste your time.
